From 07524659e6bc0e5948b175360651af121e760538 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursor-agent@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 17:03:53 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 01/13] Move real frontend out of backend/ to repo root

The actual UI (Login page, Dashboard, components, axios, react-router) was
incorrectly nested inside backend/imis-frontend/, while the top-level
imis-frontend/ held only the empty Create-React-App boilerplate.

This commit:
- Replaces the boilerplate top-level imis-frontend/src with the real one
- Promotes the real package.json (which has axios + react-router-dom)
- Moves school.jpg into imis-frontend/public/
- Removes the now-redundant backend/imis-frontend/ folder

After this, 'cd imis-frontend && npm install && npm start' will actually
launch the IMIS login UI on http://localhost:3000.
